searching for her,

10:02.867 --> 10:08.398
following every clue,
every hint of a clue

10:08.498 --> 10:10.766
in the process.

10:11.066 --> 10:13.798
It's exhausted me.

10:15.364 --> 10:17.663
So I'm tired.

11:31.940 --> 11:33.408
Tonight,

11:34.409 --> 11:36.773
I am yours.

11:36.873 --> 11:39.639
You may do what
you wish with me.

11:45.104 --> 11:47.206
Are you from America?

11:59.400 --> 12:03.329
