12:12.696 --> 12:15.098
What are you afraid of?

12:16.228 --> 12:19.193
The ones who grab my hands.

12:19.893 --> 12:21.909
The lost souls.

12:31.591 --> 12:33.657
Look!
They're here!

12:58.815 --> 13:01.149
I've been cursed
from birth.

13:01.249 --> 13:04.148
I feel closer to the dead
than the living.

13:04.248 --> 13:06.347
The living are the ones
who really...

13:06.447 --> 13:07.713
scare me.

13:08.613 --> 13:10.979
Been my experience that the living

13:11.079 --> 13:15.284
cause much more pain than the dead.

13:17.343 --> 13:19.958
You don't think I'm strange?

13:20.477 --> 13:23.780
