13:35.872 --> 13:38.544
You're looking for Komomo.

13:41.703 --> 13:43.544
Do you know her?

13:44.671 --> 13:49.356
If you find her, what do you plan to do?

13:49.368 --> 13:52.257
Oh, I plan...

13:52.399 --> 13:55.363
