first moment I saw her.

13:55.463 --> 13:58.328
Take her to America.
Start both our lives

13:58.428 --> 14:00.829
all over again.

14:01.029 --> 14:03.227
Give to her the life
that she deserved.

14:03.327 --> 14:05.691
