For the first time,
I took action by myself

40:26.996 --> 40:29.326
and I'm going to Hell for it.

40:29.426 --> 40:34.222
Oh, God,
I'm surrounded by madness.

40:34.522 --> 40:37.186
Suppose I'm right, though.

40:37.386 --> 40:41.916
What would the Devil think of her
having such an evil friend?

40:42.216 --> 40:44.481
He'd think if they're friends,

40:44.581 --> 40:47.146
then Komomo must be
a wicked person, too.

40:47.246 --> 40:48.978
He would've sent
her to Hell.

40:49.078 --> 40:52.076
So I aided Komomo.

40:53.076 --> 40:58.087
Now I'm sure
she's in Heaven.

40:59.526 --> 41:04.117
What could be more pitiful
to be strangled to death

41:04.217 --> 41:07.055
by the one you trusted most?

41:08.196 --> 41:12.688
I'm sure Buddha
grabbed her by the hand

41:12.688 --> 41:15.518
and took her to Heaven.

41:15.518 --> 41:18.514
Right, Sis?

41:56.766 --> 41:58.930
You're leaving
something out.

41:59.030 --> 42:01.021
You're not telling
me something!

42:01.190 --> 42:02.821
What is it?

42:03.587 --> 42:06.845
Oh, tell me!

42:06.849 --> 42:08.179
What are you hiding?

42:14.533 --> 42:16.898
Tell him the truth.

42:25.847 --> 42:28.901
Tell him the truth.

42:31.802 --> 42:33.002
No!

42:33.934 --> 42:35.330
No!

42:45.547 --> 42:47.769
You want to know.

42:47.940 --> 42:50.423
No, no, no, no,
no, no, no.

42:51.201 --> 42:53.326
I don't want to know!

42:54.764 --> 42:58.229
I need to know!

43:02.284 --> 43:04.829
Then I shall--

43:05.909 --> 43:10.117
I will tell you my story.

43:19.472 --> 43:22.456
My dadda and mama
were beggars.

43:22.792 --> 43:24.986
They called no place home.

43:27.846 --> 43:30.209
Wandering from
place to place,

43:30.309 --> 43:34.131
they ended up in the poorest
village in the region.

43:34.232 --> 43:36.025
Compared to that place,

43:36.026 --> 43:39.286
this rotten island
is paradise.

44:03.925 --> 44:06.087
Mama wasn't the midwife.

44:06.187 --> 44:07.882
She worked with babies,

44:07.982 --> 44:09.945
but she was more of
a specialist.

44:10.045 --> 44:13.369
I'm sure you have the same
practice in America, right?

44:22.445 --> 44:25.969
Ah, more sake.

44:26.269 --> 44:28.064
With what money?

44:28.164 --> 44:29.561
More sake.

44:29.661 --> 44:32.555
With what money?

44:32.655 --> 44:34.217
Sake.

44:40.867 --> 44:43.287
No, no!
Look at me.

44:43.161 --> 44:44.957
Aah!

44:48.216 --> 44:50.497
No, stop!
No!

44:57.592 --> 45:00.786
Okay!  No, no!

45:00.985 --> 45:03.644
No! Oh!

45:03.744 --> 45:04.875
Aah!

45:04.975 --> 45:06.171
Sake.

45:11.590 --> 45:14.284
Sake.

45:14.984 --> 45:18.041
Despite his cruelty
and drinking,

45:18.141 --> 45:20.770
Mama did her duties
as a good wife.

45:20.870 --> 45:23.625
She soon got pregnant with me.

46:20.021 --> 46:22.350
You asked for the truth.

46:22.450 --> 46:29.019
Yes, I was dumped in the
river and left to die, too.

46:35.318 --> 46:40.804
But two days later, I was
still alive and kicking.

46:43.001 --> 46:46.292
Mama made up her mind
to raise me.

47:05.943 --> 47:08.768
As long as I can remember,

47:08.868 --> 47:11.962
I helped Mama with her work.

47:24.097 --> 47:25.127
Unh!

48:11.016 --> 48:13.343
Dump this.

48:13.343 --> 48:19.693
That hole is the one
that leads to Hell.

48:21.357 --> 48:23.751
Pretty scary, huh?

48:29.004 --> 48:32.994
If you don't do as I say,

48:33.094 --> 48:36.340
you will go
straight to Hell.

48:44.132 --> 48:50.843
And so this hole
leads to Hell, too.

48:50.878 --> 48:52.280
Freak!

48:53.578 --> 48:55.863
Baby killer!

48:55.898 --> 48:56.997
Beggar!

48:57.032 --> 48:58.214
Freak!

48:58.249 --> 49:00.378
Freak! Freak! Freak!

49:00.413 --> 49:02.413
Go away,
you little brats!

49:27.263 --> 49:30.599
No! No! No! No!

49:32.382 --> 49:33.480
No! No!

49:33.580 --> 49:35.672
Stop!  Stop it!

49:39.728 --> 49:41.745
Aah! Stop!

49:41.780 --> 49:42.501
Go on!

49:42.536 --> 49:43.555
No!

49:43.555 --> 49:45.865
Oh! No!

51:40.465 --> 51:42.431
Stop this!

52:01.338 --> 52:03.247
No, Sis.

52:05.296 --> 52:06.363
Aah!

52:58.756 --> 53:00.419
Sis!

53:00.419 --> 53:03.886
Stop it, Sis.

53:04.586 --> 53:05.754
Bitch!

53:07.154 --> 53:10.004
My twin.

53:12.252 --> 53:14.929
Have I got your attention, Mister?

53:16.484 --> 53:20.708
Yes, I'm a twin

53:21.683 --> 53:24.082
and this is my sister.

53:30.950 --> 53:35.147
Nobody ever knew
about my sister.

53:35.347 --> 53:36.248
Nobody...

53:36.348 --> 53:37.915
Aah!

53:38.115 --> 53:39.514
...except Mama.

53:39.614 --> 53:40.213
Aah!

53:40.313 --> 53:43.658
Oh, she knew.

53:43.693 --> 53:44.929
Aah!

53:49.359 --> 53:50.633
No!

53:50.745 --> 53:52.385
Stop it, Brother!

53:52.984 --> 53:54.077
Unh!

53:54.679 --> 53:57.605
It turned out
that Mama and Dada

53:57.705 --> 54:00.220
were brother and sister.

54:00.226 --> 54:00.996
Sake.

54:01.097 --> 54:05.288
People found out and
ran them out of town.

54:05.490 --> 54:08.415
While begging their way
across the country,

54:08.746 --> 54:11.105
they escaped to this place.

54:11.439 --> 54:14.169
My sister and I were cursed

54:14.269 --> 54:16.728
long before
coming into this world.

