56:38.654 --> 56:39.941
Oh.

56:39.941 --> 56:43.917
Oh, I should never have come here.
This place...

56:44.439 --> 56:49.917
This place is truly
a damned place!

56:49.952 --> 56:53.541
No matter where you go,
your hell follows you.

56:53.641 --> 56:57.106
I know what you did
back in America.

57:01.106 --> 57:02.604
