57:10.206 --> 57:11.571
Why?"

57:12.970 --> 57:15.702
You freak.
You freak!

57:15.802 --> 57:17.736
Freak! Freak!

57:20.138 --> 57:23.900
Okay, you win.

57:27.302 --> 57:31.233
